ul.li:
Both HP Linux for HP Helion OpenStack and HP Helion OpenStack are part of the ISO you
          will download from the Helion Downloads page. There is only one download;
          it includes both the operating system and the Helion OpenStack installer in one ISO.

ol.li:
 Add the cloud deployment definition to the git
          :cd /home/stack/helion/hos/ansible;
git add -A;
git commit -m 'Adding ESX Configurations or other commit message';

Prepare your environment for deployment:
          ansible-playbook -i hosts/localhost config-processor-run.yml;
ansible-playbook -i hosts/localhost ready-deployment.yml;
cd /home/stack/scratch/ansible/next/hos/ansible;
